page.title: 14BIRDS IN THE WOLDS
page.content: { Common birds include : Dunnock Blackbird Song Thrush Robin Wren House Sparrow Starling Sky-lark Yellow Hammer Magpie Lapwing Willow Warbler Pheasant Partridge Wood Pigeon Swallow House Martin Swift Cuckoo Carrion Crow Mallard & Coot Mute Swan Collared Dove Moorhen Blue Tit Pied Wagtail Great Tit Rook Black-headed & Herring Gull {Less Common :} Tawny, Little & Barn Owl Linnet Marsh, Coal & Long-tailed tit Kestrel Reed & Sedge Warbler Jay Green, Gold, Bull & Chaffinch Redwing Reed Bunting Water Rail Redstart Tree Sparrow Mistle Thrush Redshank Gold Crest Whitethroat Kingfisher Yellow Wagtail {Rare :} Short-eared Owl Snipe Sparrow Hawk Winchat
